curam.util.ctm.bom

Interface DependentBOM

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BusinessObjectModule
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ApplicationConfigDependentBOMImpl, AppResourceDependentBOMImpl, CodeTableDependentBOMImpl, CodeTableHierarchyDependentBOMImpl, CSSAppResourceDependentBOMImpl, EventDependentBOMImpl, ImageAppResourceDependentBOMImpl, PropertiesAppResourceDependentBOMImpl, PropertiesDependentBOMImpl, RulesDependentBOMImpl, SchemaAppResourceDependentBOMImpl, SectionConfigDependentBOMImpl, SecurityGroupDependentBOMImpl, SecurityIdentifierDependentBOMImpl, SecurityRoleDependentBOMImpl, TabConfigDependentBOMImpl, XMLAppResourceDependentBOMImpl, XSLTemplateDependentBOMImpl

    public interface DependentBOM
extends BusinessObjectModule

    Infrastructure delegates to DependentBOM implementation to populate list of all immediate dependent business object.

    DependentBOM is an optional BOM. Individual BOM implementation would need to decide if they have immediate dependency on any other business object instance. If Business object module doesn't have a DependentBOM implementation it is understood by infrastructure as BOM can be transported to another system by itself.
